parameters:
\n<Rui-chan>"I haven't forgotten anything. Wadsworth, we won't be able
to return home for a while."
\n<Wadsworth>"Yeah, it's all good. Let's go before we get caught."

\n<Rui-chan>"We should head as far away as possible. It would be best to
find a town where our names aren't known. A region where
beastfolk are rare would be ideal."

\n<Wadsworth>"Then let's head to the Adventurers' Guild! That way, we're
sure to hear news about my sister!"

\n<Rui-chan>"Father is going to be furious. I'd love to see the look on
his face!"

\n<Wadsworth>"Yeah. But, I wonder if grandpa will be okay? I wouldn't
like it if he got scolded because of us."
\n<Rui-chan>"Let's buy a new vase on our way back."
